        "parameters": {
          "width": 460,
          "height": 220,
          "content": "## General 3D Presentation\nThis workflow creates 360° or 180° spinning videos of high-quality 3D models with [PiAPI]({{ $env.API_BASE_URL }} API. 🙋\n### Required Instruction: \n1. Fill in params of Prompt node.\n2. Fill in x-api-key in Mijdourney Generator node and Generate Kling Video node, fill in Header Parameters of GPT-4o Image Generator (e.g., Bearer + your X-API-Key)"
